Literature Survey Summary
 
## Chatbots in Education
- Used for answering FAQs, guiding students, and automating admin tasks.
- Improve engagement and reduce manual effort.
 
## Web-Based Chatbot Solutions
- Often rely on NLP and ML models.
- Require training data and backend infrastructure.
 
## Gemini API Integration
- Uses structured documents for response generation.
- Avoids NLP complexity, ideal for educational settings.
 
## Challenges
- Ensuring accuracy and relevance
- Handling diverse queries
- Maintaining updated content
 
## Related Work
- Chatbots in university portals
- Hybrid models using APIs and ML
